py-cpanel - Python interface to manage cpanel domains

Author: Ítalo Rossi 
Email:   italorossib@gmail.com
Version: 0.1alpha

Documentation

>>> from cpaneldomain import CpanelDomain
>>> my_domain = CpanelDomain("domain.com")
>>> my.domain.contactemail
'contact@domain.com'
>>> my_domain.suspended
False
>>> my_domain.email_accounts
 {'email_1': {'used_space': 11829248, 'quota_limit': 209715200}, 'email_2': {'used_space': 11816960, 'quota_limit': 104857600}
 
Methods implemented:

    admin_user
    contactemail
    domain_name
    email_accounts
    hosting_plan
    quota_limit
    redirects
    suspended
    used_bandwidth
    used_space
    
Feel free to submit bugs and feature requests.
